quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaññani ɓendre mun nden, fii lislaamu, hara himo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii ɓen yooruɓe ɓerɗe mun, e jantagol Allah. Ɓen wonii e majjere ɓanngunde"
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko ɓuri moƴƴude e yewtere, Deftere nanndunde [ñaawooje], ɗimmitunde. Nde guri ɓen hulooɓe Joomi mun riɓirta (nanugol nde), refti guri e ɓerɗe maɓɓe deeƴira jantoore Allah nden. Ko ɗum woni peewal Allah ngal O fewnirta on Mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo mo alaa"
  39,24,"E ko on reentariiɗo yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bonɗe ɗen Ñalnde Darngal... Tooñuɓe ɓen wi'anee ontuma: \"Meeɗee kon ko wonunoɗon faggitanaade"
  39,25,"Adinooɓe ɓen fenniino, lepte ɗen ardirani ɓe, ka ɓe so'aa-anndude"
  39,26,"Allah meeɗiniri ɓe koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte laakara ɗen non, ɓuri mawnude, si tawno hiɓe anndunoo"
  39,27,"Gomɗii Men piyanii yimɓe ɓen, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, belajo'o, ɓe waajitora"
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e ooñaare, fii no ɓe gomɗira"
  39,29,"Allah waɗii misal, gorko mo lurruɓe hawti ɗum, hiɓe pooɗondira mo, e gorko laaɓanɗo gorko [goo]: Hara ɓen ɗiɗo fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono ɓurɓe ɗuuɗude e maɓɓe, ɓe anndaa"
  39,30,"Pellet, ko a maayoowo, kamɓe kadi ko ɓe maayooɓe"
  39,31,"refti onon, Ñalnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon, yeddondiroyton"